01:33.410 --> 01:35.032
Welcome to all of our campuses.

01:35.432 --> 01:37.936
Welcome to our eFam all around the world.

01:38.516 --> 01:42.221
I'm sending you a hug across the internet.

01:42.241 --> 01:43.142
A worldwide hug.

01:44.443 --> 01:46.346
Let us know where you're joining from, would you?

01:47.367 --> 01:49.450
Just put your city and your state and your name.

01:50.691 --> 01:51.853
Maybe your favorite candy.

01:52.774 --> 01:53.214
I don't know.

01:54.616 --> 01:57.760
Put on the list if you had a good Valentine's weekend.

01:57.800 --> 01:59.802
If you celebrate that kind of pagan holiday.

02:00.763 --> 02:01.244
I was playing.

02:02.285 --> 02:02.866
I was playing.

02:05.122 --> 02:05.903
I was playing.

